/// test group: input controls
/// test purpose: sample selection based on pitch bend position
///
/// test description:
/// 440.wav will play if bend wheel is in the positive range
/// 110.wav will play if bend wheel is in the negative range
/// no region will play when bend is centered

<group> bend_up=0 bend_down=0
<region> sample=..\[ samples ]\440.wav lobend=1 hibend=8192
<region> sample=..\[ samples ]\110.wav lobend=-8192 hibend=-1